type: TS Trading Session Error - Final Datetime Is Not A Valid Date

definition.text: The finalDatetime property configured at the Time Range node is not recongnized as a valid Javascript Datetime.

paragraphs.text: The validation of sessionParameters.timeRange.config.finalDatetime did not pass, and therefore the Trading Session can not run.
Check Node JS Javsacript docs to learn how to correctly express a datetime value.
